Sample FlightRadar24's archived feed ADS-B flight data for EGLL.

Source: R/data.R
egll_flights_fr24.Rd

A dataset containing FlightRadar24's archived feed ADS-B flight information for XX flights. There are xx flights on d1 and yy on yy.

Usage

egll_flights_fr24

Format

A data frame with xxyy rows and 11 variables:

address

mode-S address in hexadecimal, as supplied by the Mode-S or ADS-B transponder

adep

ICAO code for scheduled departure airport

ades

ICAO code for scheduled arrival airport

callsign

e.g. CSA190, as supplied by the Mode-S or ADS-B transponder

flight_id

unique identifier for the flight leg (integer)

reg

unique aircraft identifier (text)

model

aircraft type (e.g. B733, as per ICAO classification?), GLID for gliders, GROUND for ground vehicles

flight

flight number, e.g. OK190

start_time

date of the flight (what about the ones crssing midnight?)

Source

FlightRadar24
